  {
    "type": "EXEGETICAL (ORIGINAL LANGUAGES)",
    "name": "Pulpit Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_sub_title",
        "text": "Verse 4.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "I said.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " It is doubtful who is the speaker. Professor Cheyne regards the entire passage from the beginning of ver. 2 to the end of ver. 5 as spoken by the Almighty; but most commentators assign vers. 4 and 5 to the psalmist or the people of Israel. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Unto the fools",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " to the enemy which was attacking Israel; literally, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "to the boasters",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", or ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "to the arrogant ones",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " (see Revised Version). ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Deal not foolishly;",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " rather, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "deal not so arrogantly.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Do not set yourselves so proudly against the Almighty. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "And to the wicked, Lift not up the horn;",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "accented",
        "text": "i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " be not fierce and menacing, like a bull who threatens with his horns. Psalm 75:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
